@1:00 - 
I've actually done that.. alone.. multiple times.. 🤦‍♀️ in my 20s I traveled outside of my country many times.. I was a free-spirit and looked at each and every trip as an adventure.  I got very lucky many times and I now know that.  I never thought of myself as naive either.. actually quite the opposite..  thought I was pretty smart but now with the internet and realizing just how easily things can happen and how close I came, too many times.. it's crazy but of course I consider myself extremely fortunate.  
I have a lot of great memories and cherish each one but I also had a lot of close calls and could tell stories for days.. thankfully nothing turned out as bad as it could have and I will never take that for granted.
